Package com.mathmaster13.fynotek

package com.mathmaster13.fynotek
Provides classes for working with words in Fynotek. More information on Fynotek can be found here. This project's source code can be found on GitHub.

This project is still in development, and features may be changed or removed at any time.
Version:
3.0
Author:
mathmaster13
